name: Wellzesta
0:
”Alexa, open Dory assistant”
”Alexa, ask Dory assistant to give me my daily summary”
”Alexa, ask Dory assistant to list my messages”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: dory assistant
Developer Terms of Use
des:
The Wellzesta skill on Alexa helps you access community events and messages, using your voice! Wellzesta uses our built in Dory assistant to:

- give you a daily summary of events
- tell you about your day
- read your messages and events

Get started with Wellzesta on Alexa!
1. Ask Alexa to open "Dory assistant".
2. Try out a phrase, such as: 
 "Ask Dory Assistant to Tell me about my day."
 "Ask Dory Assistant to Are there any updates for me today?"
 "Ask Dory Assistant to Give me my daily summary."
 "Ask Dory Assistant about my events."
 "Ask Dory Assistant to list my messages."
